TI  - Nicotinamide Mononucleotide and Nicotinamide Riboside Improve Dyslipidemia and Fatty Liver but Promote Atherosclerosis in Apolipoprotein E Knockout Mice
PY  - 2025
T2  - Pharmaceuticals
VL  - 18
IS  - 3
C7  - 281
