TI  - The effects of NAD+ precursor (nicotinic acid and nicotinamide) supplementation on weight loss and related hormones: a systematic review and meta-regression analysis of randomized controlled trials
PY  - 2023
T2  - Frontiers in Nutrition
VL  - 10
C7  - 1208734
DO  - 10.3389/fnut.2023.1208734
