TI  - Inhibition of nicotinamide phosphoribosyltransferase (NAMPT) with OT-82 induces DNA damage, cell death, and suppression of tumor growth in preclinical models of Ewing sarcoma
PY  - 2020
T2  - Oncogenesis
VL  - 9
IS  - 9
